{"name":"Adalene Caressa","size":"medium","type":"humanoid","tag":"Grand Council, Mystra","alignment":"Lawful Neutral","hitDice":"15","armorName":"mage armor","shieldBonus":0,"natArmorBonus":-9,"otherArmorDesc":"10","speed":"30","burrowSpeed":"0","climbSpeed":"0","flySpeed":"0","hover":false,"swimSpeed":"0","customHP":false,"customSpeed":false,"hpText":"22 (5d8)","speedDesc":"30 ft.","strPoints":"8","dexPoints":"16","conPoints":"12","intPoints":"18","wisPoints":"20","chaPoints":"12","blindsight":"0","blind":false,"darkvision":"30","tremorsense":"0","truesight":"0","telepathy":0,"cr":"7","customCr":"1 (200 XP)","customProf":2,"isLegendary":false,"legendariesDescription":"The monster can take 3 legendary actions, choosing from the options below. Only one legendary action option can be used at a time and only at the end of another creature's turn. The monster regains spent legendary actions at the start of its turn.","isLair":false,"lairDescription":"When fighting inside its lair, the monster can invoke the ambient magic to take lair actions. On initiative count 20 (losing initiative ties), the monster can take one lair action to cause one of the following effects:","lairDescriptionEnd":"The monster can't repeat an effect until they have all been used, and it can't use the same effect two rounds in a row.","isMythic":false,"mythicDescription":"If the monster's mythic trait is active, it can use the options below as legendary actions for 1 hour after using {Some Ability}.","isRegional":false,"regionalDescription":"The region containing the monster's lair is warped by the creature's presence, which creates one or more of the following effects:","regionalDescriptionEnd":"If the monster dies, the first two effects fade over the course of 3d10 days.","properties":[],"abilities":[{"name":"Quick Cast","desc":"[MON] may set the casting time for any of her spells to an action."},{"name":"Paragon of Magic","desc":"[MON] can cast **any** spells at or below 5th level. [MON] may channel divinity once per long rest to cast **any** spells at or below 7th level. [MON]'s spellcasting ability is wisdom ([WIS SAVE] to save, [WIS ATK] to hit). Here's some suggested spells:\n\n> Cantrips (at will): _Fire Bolt, Shocking Grasp, Sacred Flame_\n> 1st level (4 slots): _Chromatic Orb, Magic Missile, Mage Armor, Shield, Detect Magic_\n> 2nd level (3 slots): _Lesser Restoration, Misty Step, Melf's Acid Arrows_\n> 3rd level (3 slots): _Counterspell, Dispel Magic, Glyph of Warding, Magic Circle_\n> 4th level (3 slots): _Dimension Door, Ice Storm, Blight_\n> 5th level (1 slot): _Creation, Teleportation Circle, Geas, Hallow_\n> 6th level (special): _Globe of Invulnerability, Disintegrate_\n> 7th level (special): _Symbol, Crown of Stars_"}],"actions":[],"bonusActions":[],"reactions":[],"legendaries":[],"mythics":[],"lairs":[],"regionals":[],"sthrows":[{"name":"int","order":3},{"name":"wis","order":4}],"skills":[{"name":"arcana","stat":"int","note":" (ex)"},{"name":"religion","stat":"int","note":" (ex)"}],"damagetypes":[],"specialdamage":[],"conditions":[],"languages":[],"understandsBut":"","shortName":"Adalene","pluralName":"","doubleColumns":true,"separationPoint":0,"damage":[]}